{"tid":354810,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"東亞個網上銀行真係垃撚圾","createTime":"2017-08-10T18:28:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-11T13:07:37.000Z","uid":53209,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2e225c3106b8a68c8a740ab37cfa4f484ab7e8a7","tid":354810,"uid":53209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T18:28:08.000Z","msg":"早輪 開左張東亞信用卡 自然有個 網上銀行AC<br />\n近期因為有需要用 而開埋東亞銀行AC 個陣又係攪左一個網上銀行AC<br />\n好似叫咩I-ACCOUNT之類既 因為平時唔會用東亞既銀行戶口 所以開左 轉左唔收紙版月結單之後就無理過 只係用信用卡戶口<br />\n<br />\n最近手痕禁下啦諗住 我發現居然 經東亞個官網 「登入」-&gt;「電子網絡銀行服務」 之類 入面有得簡 信用卡/銀行卡 等等既野 然後我點「銀行卡」個到 係話我無佢地銀行既戶口  即係 信用卡戶口 同銀行戶口係分開 乜撚野垃圾系統咁弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ? 間銀行幾撚時汁粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"255201fd5b09592e3e35786a0184818bc2a65550","tid":354810,"uid":69083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T18:34:16.000Z","msg":"有咩問題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f33d34a371e7a83608c198883020dbcfbc58a992","tid":354810,"uid":54576,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T18:37:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca8dad974c7901ad8c00fb966c2fdafb0282cd9c","tid":354810,"uid":53209,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T18:45:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有咩問題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁都無問題?<br />\n佢個網上銀行戶口入面 有銀行卡 依一個部份比我簡<br />\n但係點入去 居然話無資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有用 HSBC 渣打 BOC 全部都係 合埋做同一個網上AC 方便管理"},{"pid":"808c30a6fceaaa77c17af8c6f79226192202cfd4","tid":354810,"uid":105856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T18:52:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有咩問題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁都無問題?<br />\n佢個網上銀行戶口入面 有銀行卡 依一個部份比我簡<br /